text: Sorry, just seeing this. There is currently an issue uploading when you’re using an APIKEY. Personal access keys are now the recommended auth method, so I would recommend switching to that
We’ve got a fix in the works to enable uploading with api key auth, though so that will work once again soon, you’ll just need to upgrade your CLI to the latest version
